    "As the use of GPT models and other language generation technologies continues to grow, it becomes increasingly vital to ensure that these systems are equipped to handle gender and promote inclusivity.",
    "Our research aims to contribute to the ongoing efforts to make MT systems more equitable and sensitive to issues of gender representation.",
    "In closing, this chapter has shed light on the challenges posed by gender bias in MT.",
    "It emphasizes the need for continued multidisciplinary research, advancements, and collaborative endeavors to pave the way towards more equitable and unbiased language technologies.",
    "As the field progresses, we hope to see the transformation of MT systems into powerful tools that promote diversity, inclusivity, and societal progress."
